{"word":"παρέχω","slug":"παρέχω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>παρέχω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:παρά\">παρά</a>, <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἔχω\">ἔχω</a></el>] ‘cause <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ someth.\">someth.</a> to be present for the other’<b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> focus on negative aspect, <b>inflict <a href='B:470 26:10'>Mt 26:10</a>; <a href='B:480 14:6'>Mk 14:6</a>; <a href='B:490 11:7'>Lk 11:7</a>; <a href='B:490 18:5'>18:5</a>; <a href='B:550 6:17'>Gal 6:17</a>; bring about <a href='B:610 1:4'>1 Ti 1:4</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> focus on positive aspect<b> bring about, furnish <a href='B:510 16:16'>Ac 16:16</a>; <a href='B:510 17:31'>17:31</a>; <a href='B:510 19:24'>19:24</a>; <a href='B:510 22:2'>22:2</a>; <a href='B:510 28:2'>28:2</a>; <a href='B:610 6:17'>1 Ti 6:17</a>; <a href='B:630 2:7'>Tit 2:7</a>; do <a href='B:490 7:4'>Lk 7:4</a>; ensure <a href='B:580 4:1'>Col 4:1</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:παρέτεινεν\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:παρήγγειλα\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}